meta-embedded - Custom Embedded Linux Layer
============================================

This layer provides custom recipes and configurations for embedded
Linux applications built with the Yocto Project.

Supported Release: scarthgap

Contents:
- recipes-myapp:    Custom application recipes
- recipes-kernel:   Out-of-tree kernel module recipes
- recipes-core:     Custom image recipes

Dependencies:
- poky/meta (core metadata)
- poky/meta-poky (Poky distribution)

Usage:
  1. Add to bblayers.conf:
     BBLAYERS += "${TOPDIR}/../meta-embedded"

  2. Set layer priority (default: 10):
     BBFILE_PRIORITY_embedded = "10"

Maintainer: Embedded Linux Training
